      "instruction": "<p>Trim your <strong>green beans</strong>, then add them to a pot with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min or until tender</p><p>Once done, drain, then set aside for serving</p>",
